## Validation Error Response

When a request fails validation, the server returns a structured `400` response:

```json
{
  "status": 400,
  "error": "Validation Failed",
  "message": "Request body has N validation error(s)",
  "path": "/api/...",
  "timestamp": "2026-01-01T00:00:00",
  "validationErrors": [
    {
      "field": "fieldName",
      "message": "error description",
      "rejectedValue": null
    }
  ]
}
```

