## Testing

The generated server includes a comprehensive test suite covering **three layers**:

### Run All Tests

```bash
mvn test
```

### Test Layers

| Layer | Annotation | Description |
| ----- | ---------- | ----------- |
| **Controller** | `@SpringBootTest` + `@AutoConfigureMockMvc` | Full integration tests using MockMvc. Tests all CRUD endpoints and validation rules. |
| **Service** | `@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)` | Unit tests with mocked repository. Verifies business logic and exception handling. |
| **Repository** | `@DataJpaTest` | JPA tests with embedded H2 database. Verifies persistence operations. |
| **Application** | `@SpringBootTest` | Smoke test — verifies the Spring context loads without errors. |

